                {
                    "id": "unstable_kzz_piece4_above_bl",
                    "description": "Unstable K_zz (Eq. 18.121), piece 4 — above the boundary layer z/z_i > 1.1. At z = 1200 m, L_MO = -100 m (z/z_i = 1.2) K_zz collapses to the residual constant wzi*0.0013. Reproduces piece 4 of the upstream `Unstable K_zz (Eq. 18.121)` testitem.",
