                {
                    "id": "neutral_kzz_surface_layer",
                    "description": "Neutral K_zz (Eq. 18.122, Myrup & Ranzieri 1976), surface-layer branch z/z_i < 0.1. L_MO = 1.0e6 m gives |L_MO/z_i| = 1000 > 10, selecting the neutral profile; at z = 50 m (z/z_i = 0.05) K_zz = kappa*u_star*z = 0.4*0.3*50 = 6.0 m^2/s. Reproduces the surface-layer assertion of the upstream `Neutral K_zz (Eq. 18.122)` testitem.",
                    "parameter_overrides": {
                        "z": 50.0,
                        "L_MO": 1000000.0
                    },
                    "time_span": {
                        "start": 0.0,
                        "end": 1.0
