                            }
                        },
                        {
                            "variable": "K_yy",
                            "time": 0.0,
                            "expected": 0.0,
                            "tolerance": {
                                "abs": 1e-12
                            }
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "id": "stable_kzz_surface",
                    "description": "Stable K_zz (Eq. 18.125, Businger & Arya 1974) near the surface. L_MO = 200 m gives L_MO/z_i = 0.2 (0 < |L_MO/z_i| <= 10 and L_MO/z_i > 0), selecting the stable profile K_zz = kappa*u_star*z/(0.74 + 4.7 z/L) * exp(-8 f z/u_star). Evaluated at z = 50 m. Reproduces the z=50 assertion of the upstream `Stable K_zz (Eq. 18.125)` testitem.",
                    "parameter_overrides": {
