                    "id": "stable_kzz_aloft",
                    "description": "Stable K_zz (Eq. 18.125) higher in the stable boundary layer. L_MO = 200 m selects the stable profile; evaluated at z = 200 m, where the (0.74 + 4.7 z/L) denominator growth and the exp(-8 f z/u_star) decay together hold K_zz well below its surface value. Reproduces the z=200 assertion of the upstream `Stable K_zz (Eq. 18.125)` testitem.",
                    "parameter_overrides": {
