                    "description": "Vertical eddy diffusivity profile under neutral conditions (L_MO = 1.0e6 m, so |L_MO/z_i| = 1000 >> 10 selects the neutral branch), swept over height z from 10 to 1500 m. K_zz follows the Myrup & Ranzieri (1976) profile of Eq. 18.122 — linear growth kappa*u_star*z through the surface layer, the kappa*u_star*z*(1.1 - z/z_i) roll-off through the mixed layer, and zero above z/z_i = 1.1. Reproduces the docs `Figure 18.7: Neutral K_zz Profile`.",
